title: Act As If
itunes:title: Act As If
description:
Episode 191 -  This is the second part to Episode 190 "Grow Into Yourself" In order to become the person that you want to be you must first start acting like that person and developing their habits. In this episode I talk about how to do that and how to develop key habits to change your life right now.
